1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:02,850
How dare you!

3
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:03,800
In front of the Empress Dowager,

4
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:05,960
how can you speak so disrespectfully?

5
00:01:07,240 --> 00:01:08,960
This girl is so outspoken.

6
00:01:09,160 --> 00:01:10,360
Interesting.

7
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,800
No wonder she works so well

8
00:01:11,800 --> 00:01:12,800
with this boy.

9
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:13,840
They complement each other

10
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,280
and have solved several major cases.

11
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,960
She is indeed a rare woman

12
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:20,400
in this world.

13
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:22,360
You flatter me, Your Grace.

14
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:25,360
There are countless women better than me in this world.

15
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:26,560
I am just lucky enough

16
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:29,160
to have the chance to do what I love.

17
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:30,080
Yes.

18
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:31,820
How many women in the world

19
00:01:31,960 --> 00:01:33,080
cannot control their own destiny

20
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:35,200
from birth?

21
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,680
You can do as you please.

22
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:38,680
I am

23
00:01:38,759 --> 00:01:40,320
a little jealous.

24
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:41,880
Never mind.

25
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,160
Liu Chuan,

26
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,200
tell me,

27
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,060
what exactly do you want to do?

28
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,440
To reply to the Empress Dowager,

29
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:50,259
according to my observation,

30
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,360
someone dies

31
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,610
every twelve hours.

32
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:54,200
Locking them up now

33
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,759
is actually a good thing.

34
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,280
Do you have a way?

35
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,240
Let me give it a try.

36
00:01:59,440 --> 00:02:00,160
Try?

37
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,920
This is a matter of great importance.

38
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,520
How can you treat it as a game?

39
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:07,290
Then do you have a better idea, Your Highness?

40
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,720
Consort De,

41
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:13,440
you are usually eloquent,

42
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,160
but when it comes to arguing,

43
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,760
you are no match for this boy.

44
00:02:17,400 --> 00:02:18,760
Then tell me,

45
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,200
how are you going to try?

46
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,720
Since it involves professional pathology

47
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,800
and virus testing,

48
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:25,520
I need someone to assist me.

49
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,160
Who?

50
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,240
Gu Zhengyan.

51
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,640
Mother, absolutely not.

52
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:31,240
Gu Zhengyan is also on the Book of Life and Death.

53
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,960
He is clearly friends with Gu Zhengyan privately

54
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,000
and wants to let him go secretly.

55
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,760
What if missing Gu Zhengyan

56
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,440
causes the Ziwei Star to become unstable?

57
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,970
Wouldn't that be terrible?

58
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,480
There is King Jia.

59
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:43,000
With him and his well-trained guards watching,

60
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,120
who could escape?

61
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:46,160
Prince Jia.

62
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:56,220
I will follow the Empress Dowager's orders.

63
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,400
You are lucky.

64
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,280
To have someone at a critical moment

65
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:02,680
who stands by you.

66
00:03:03,680 --> 00:03:05,120
Someone who dares to challenge

67
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,760
Consort De for you.

68
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,760
Sister Empress Dowager.

69
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:09,480
Qiuyue

70
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:11,120
is not only my partner

71
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:14,740
but also a confidant I trust with my life.

72
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,560
She is also the one I am willing to protect

73
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,490
with all my heart for my whole life.

74
00:03:22,480 --> 00:03:23,360
Qiuyue.

75
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:25,280
I give you a token

76
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:28,400
that allows you to walk freely in the palace

77
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,120
so that you can report

78
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,960
the case to me at any time.

79
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:32,840
Besides,

80
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,160
I also want to hear

81
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:37,000
about your anecdotes as a constable

82
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,360
for

83
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,120
entertainment.

84
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,720
I obey your command.

85
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,400
Come here.

86
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,760
I presume

87
00:03:55,760 --> 00:03:57,360
you've been in the palace for years.

88
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,440
You must have amassed quite a fortune.

89
00:03:59,440 --> 00:03:59,960
Look,

90
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:02,000
Death is coming for you soon.

91
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,520
You can't take it with you.

92
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,000
How about this?

93
00:04:06,000 --> 00:04:07,560
You give it to me,

94
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:08,760
and before you die,

95
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:10,360
I'll let you have a good meal.

96
00:04:10,720 --> 00:04:12,240
Otherwise...

97
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:16,440
Speak.

98
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,399
I'll talk.

99
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:23,120
They are all under the banyan tree behind my house.

100
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,080
Go.

101
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,410
So young and beautiful.

102
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,240
It'd be a pity if you died.

103
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,159
My lord.

104
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:38,840
You might as well let me enjoy you.

105
00:04:38,960 --> 00:04:39,760
No, my lord!

106
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,360
Insolent!

107
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,960
Who gave you the nerve

108
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,159
to be so reckless?

109
00:04:49,440 --> 00:04:52,120
Aren't you afraid the Emperor and the Empress Dowager will blame you?

110
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,480
Isn't this Lord Gu?

111
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:54,280
What?

112
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:56,159
The Empress Dowager,

113
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:57,000
the Emperor.

114
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,840
You speak of the Empress Dowager and the Emperor.

115
00:04:59,840 --> 00:05:00,840
Where are they?

116
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:01,640
Where?

117
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:02,760
Do you think

118
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:04,240
they will still care about

119
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,360
a bunch of dying people like you?

120
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:08,360
My martial uncle will definitely resolve this tribulation.

121
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,360
When Death comes knocking,

122
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,600
who can escape?

123
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,000
Let me give you some advice.

124
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,060
Stop daydreaming.

125
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:15,010
Gu Zhengyan.

126
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,800
You usually act so high and mighty.

127
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:18,440
Today, I'll make you beg on your knees.

128
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:18,900
Come on.

129
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:29,360
What?

130
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,360
Still defiant?

131
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,240
Let me tell you.

132
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,500
You are just like them.

133
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,720
I don't care what you were like before.

134
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,960
Now that you're in my hands,

135
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:38,120
I can crush you easily.

136
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:40,560
Oh, right.

137
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,080
You feel sorry for this old eunuch, don't you?

138
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:42,760
Fine.

139
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,280
Then I'll

140
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:45,159
make you

141
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,280
just like him.

142
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,500
Don't you dare!

143
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,700
Take off his pants.

144
00:05:50,960 --> 00:05:51,520
Stop.

145
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,000
Uncle.

146
00:05:54,200 --> 00:05:54,880
Step aside.

147
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:55,680
Uncle.

148
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,120
Good thing I arrived in time.

149
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:59,050
Are my nephew and niece still here?

150
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:00,560
Yes, they are.

151
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,240
Liu Chuan.

152
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,560
How dare you

153
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,360
cause trouble here!

154
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:03,840
Guards!

155
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:04,690
Capture him.

156
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:10,600
Guards!

157
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:12,040
Go!

158
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,840
By the Emperor's decree,

159
00:06:18,840 --> 00:06:20,840
anyone who causes trouble in the palace

160
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:21,640
will be killed

161
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,240
without mercy.

162
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:22,970
Capture him.

163
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,840
You really take yourself too seriously,

164
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:25,320
sir.

165
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,240
By order of the Empress Dowager,

166
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:30,160
Gu Zhengyan is permitted to assist Liu Chuan.

167
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:31,760
He is to be released immediately.

168
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,490
In addition,

169
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,880
the others temporarily in custody

170
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:34,960
must be treated properly.

171
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:35,960
Anyone who acts out of personal spite

172
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,020
will not be spared.

173
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,240
You lowly constable!

174
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,200
How dare you fake the Empress Dowager's decree!

175
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,159
The token is fake!

176
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:46,800
Take them down!

177
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,930
Let's see who dares!

178
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,159
You really won't give up

179
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:50,400
until you hit a dead end.

180
00:06:50,400 --> 00:06:51,600
Bring it on, brother!

181
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,360
Since I entered the palace,

182
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:54,760
I haven't been in a fight.

183
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:00,760
I said,

184
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,160
kill them all!

185
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,900
Greetings, Empress Dowager.

186
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,000
Empress Dowager.

187
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,360
Liuchuan,

188
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,800
the person has been released.

189
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,760
What will

190
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,160
you do next?

191
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,360
Empress Dowager,

192
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,600
I will check everyone,

193
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,530
and then conduct

194
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:24,010
targeted inspections.

195
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:27,850
Are you that confident?

196
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,160
I won't know until I try.

197
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,400
But I can't just watch

198
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,400
these people die.

199
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,280
I think the Empress Dowager feels the same way.

200
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:35,210
I have my own ways

201
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,530
to find the culprit.

202
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,400
Easier said than done.

203
00:07:40,400 --> 00:07:41,520
There are so many people in the Book of Life and Death.

204
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,380
How long will it take you to check?

205
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,960
Who was the blind fool that just said

206
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:48,020
the Empress Dowager's token is fake?

207
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,730
For each person,

208
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:51,320
I only need to take a few looks.

209
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,650
It won't take much time.

210
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,320
Empress Dowager.

211
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,040
No matter what,

212
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,440
please let Liu Chuan try.

213
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,250
They are all living people.

214
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,280
Besides, if this continues,

215
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,960
it's inevitable that people will panic

216
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,360
and cause greater chaos.

217
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:08,040
I won't give you much time.

218
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,500
You'd better hurry up.

219
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:10,440
Prince Jia.

220
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,320
Just cooperate with him.

221
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:15,960
Go.

222
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,560
Gather everyone in the courtyard.

223
00:08:17,560 --> 00:08:19,020
Do not treat them roughly.

224
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,600
Liu Chuan.

225
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:27,160
I hope you won't betray my trust.

226
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,000
I am tired.

227
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,520
Empress Dowager,

228
00:08:36,520 --> 00:08:37,450
The Director...

229
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:38,520
he was murdered.

230
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:40,440
What?

231
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,520
Could it be

232
00:08:42,760 --> 00:08:45,160
that he is also on the Book of Life and Death?

233
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,760
It was those people in the yard.

234
00:08:46,760 --> 00:08:48,640
They suddenly rushed toward the Director like crazy.

235
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,000
We

236
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,610
couldn't stop them in time.

237
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,760
This was found in the yard.

238
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,840
If you want to live,

239
00:09:03,560 --> 00:09:04,960
kill the Director first.

240
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:06,760
Could it be

241
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:09,760
because he revealed the secrets of heaven?

242
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,880
It seems the people inside,

243
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:13,280
for the hope of survival,

244
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:14,160
had no choice but to take a risk.

245
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,160
Let us out!

246
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:17,000
Hurry and let us out!

247
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:18,040
Empress Dowager,

248
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:19,040
it's not safe here.

249
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,900
Let's return to the palace first.

250
00:09:20,960 --> 00:09:21,880
Do they really

251
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,960
want to kill me?

252
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:25,410
Brother Liu.

253
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,400
Empress Dowager.

254
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,330
Leave this to me.

255
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,440
Nephew.

256
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:32,020
Go prepare at the Imperial Hospital.

257
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,560
Qiuyue, come with me.

258
00:09:47,680 --> 00:09:48,540
Your Ladyship.

259
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,160
Go.

260
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:57,760
Liu Chuan.

261
00:09:58,280 --> 00:10:00,360
Let's see what you're capable of.
